DescPackaging: <<
Does again use the in-tree version of apr since the latest released
apr is 0.9.1, which is too old for svn. Therefore svn conflicts,
replaces and provides apr and apr-shlibs

'--prefix=%p/share/svn1' is needed so that it installs the 
libtool from apr into %p/share/svn1/build and not into %p/build'
<<
